tokenInfo.title: About WEMIX
tokenInfo.desc: WEMIX is a high-performance EVM-compatible open source protocol. It operates based on the SPoA (Stake-based Proof of Authority) consensus algorithm, and this algorithm is guaranteed by 40 decentralized authority nodes run by</br>fully qualified global partners as well as on-chain community DAOs. Designed as a platform-driven, service-oriented, robust and efficient</br> public blockchain, WEMIX is the home to innovative projects and apps made by community members and used by all around the world.
